short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays a moment.js relative time for timestamps when viewing data in the Firebase console.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension uses moment.js to display a relative time against any fields that are detected as firebase timestamps when viewing data in the Firebase console.

This extension is not authorised by either Firebase or Moment.js. Use at your own risk.
